<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ludwig XI., Graf von Oettingen</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, sich wegen des Geleits für Spezerei bei den Bürgern zu erkundigen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_132" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_132_r3l10">Ludwig <expan>Graf<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>Oting<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_132_r3l11"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> des </del> geleittes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l12">von Specʒereÿ / Darvmb <expan>vvöll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir vns an den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l13">ervaren / vnd nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> vnd vvir das ervaren ewr gnad bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l14">vnſerſelbs botſchaft ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen / vnd wo etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l15"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>vitȷ</expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_132" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ludwig, <expan>Graf<ex>en</ex></expan> czü <expan>Oting<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
            habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> geleittes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> von speczerey,
            darumb <expan>wöll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir uns an den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ervaren und nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> und wir das
            ervaren ewr gnad bey unserselbs botschaft ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen. Und wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Viti</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
